Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:56.07,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}让我告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:01:04.88,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但要答应我  不会告诉其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:07.78,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}拉勾勾约好了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:13.70,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果说谎就要吃下千根针
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:32.61,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}返璞归真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:41.42,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}再次开启那个  你所熟知的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:44.38,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论是过去还是未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:51.68,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Super  scription  of  data
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.83,0:29:03.53,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不留下任何痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.48,0:29:09.24,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温柔地把你杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.01,0:29:15.84,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}换了一个词
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.48,0:29:21.68,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就把悲伤忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.57,0:29:31.66,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  现在的我到底失去了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.49,0:29:39.92,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在无尽的罪孽之中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.33,0:29:45.24,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中不禁想到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.42,0:29:51.81,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连补偿都无法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.32,0:29:57.80,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那在梦中的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.55,0:30:03.97,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那所期望的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.36,0:30:08.94,BLC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}消失不见
